extendedInfo.description: Cell # Search is now available on iPhone, iPad, and Android platforms.Fast, reliable, secure and worldwide. This is the present and future of cellular number directory.Possibly the most innovative smartphone app to date. Search any cell # on this planet, you may remain unlisted at your request and still have search capabilities. Also features reverse # look-up, email address finder, home phone numbers and of course cell number directory. No need for extra in-app purchases, no hidden costs. Once you and your friends download this app you'll appreciate the creativity of this new concept of cellular number searching.

reviews.title: Doesn\'t work.
